於 8 月 21 日為陳彥霖會診。她當日<span class=\"red\">亦診斷陳彥霖為對立反抗症</span>，為她處方鎮靜藥物，供有需要時使用，但最終醫院急症室有無為她注射鎮靜劑，鍾則表示她並不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而<span class=\"orange\">青山醫院女精神科醫生歐陽穎賢</span>今供稱，去年3月13日她於屯門醫院急症室病房與彥霖會診。彥霖當時態度冷靜平和，說話有條理、情緒穩定，沒提及有自殺或暴力行為，並否認有幻覺、幻聽或妄想症狀。歐陽指彥霖責怪社工不信守承諾，並延長她在寄宿學校的住宿時間。歐陽診斷彥霖患有急性壓力症，以及對立反抗症。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20191115/2AY4GYCYEPDYSUL65KRISXQYWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20191115%2F2AY4GYCYEPDYSUL65KRISXQYWA%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ddaa531b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20191115%2F2AY4GYCYEPDYSUL65KRISXQYWA%2F&h=2ddcc8e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20191115/2AY4GYCYEPDYSUL65KRISXQYWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【自殺之謎】同學力證彥霖失蹤前6小時仍興奮影相 無濫藥無異常 堅信彥霖非自殺"},{"pid":"6d6f32ed9d92e38a4a686f8b2f1f4c0bb3ab66f2","tid":2174554,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7839990af7f6b49d76ab5e6d33300f374dea6cc","tid":2174554,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"個醫生都係假"},{"pid":"7ab960875bc8b3174969f8e42abcdc4bd1f23434","tid":2174554,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51606b15fc01c32aab1bb6e9be2eaee754f7952f","tid":2174554,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"陪審團決定到d咩？<br />\n就算陪審團一致認為唔係自殺<br />\n咁又點？交返比班狗查？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"陪審團應該全部換晒黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efea0ebb56d2d1617d67e25cdf8fc38d4f6d5b1","tid":2174554,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0